$interpreted: Angelia: ...*heavy breathing*...why are the monsters only following our trail?
Lio: Oww, that hurt...
Angelia: Lio, get up!
Lio: Wait, my Flutterfly!
Angelia: The monsters want the gemstone in the canister...... is that it?!
Angelia: Lio, I know how to get rid of the monsters!
Lio: Really?!
Angelia: Lio, I can get rid of the monsters for sure.
Lio: REALLY?!
Angelia: Em, but...we'll, we'll have to sacrifice Flutterfly.
Lio: What?! NO! Give Flutterfly back! GIVE HIM BACK!
Angelia: Lio! I'm sad about losing Flutterfly too, but if we don't do this, everyone in the Slums will suffer.
Angelia: Is that what you want?
Lio: But... my sister isn't here, or Nigel...and Cin is...Flutterfly is all I've got!
Angelia: You're not alone. I'll be here for you. I promise I'll never to leave you behind...
Angelia: Lio, grab my necklace and put it inside Flutterfly!
Lio: Done!
Angelia: Let him soar, the farther the better! Hurry!
Lio: FLUTTERFLY! FLYYYYYY!!!!
Angelia: Whew~ I knew it, the monsters wanted Soul Energy.
Angelia: These gemstones from Totemtaff, they carry far more Soul Energy than anything else.
Lio: Flutterfly......
Angelia: Isn't the necklace's Soul Energy enough to occupy them?
Naya: Angel!
Nigel: Lio!
Nigel: Is...is it all over?
Naya: ...*heavy breathing*...the monsters have all left...
Nigel: If those soldiers would have stayed, then everyone wouldn't have...
